column10: Crossing Mt. Vernon Ave in the crosswalk heading W on my bike when a driver rolled through the red light (never stopping) to turn right from Mt. Vernon Ave onto Four Mile Rd, coming within inches of hitting me, and a pedestrian crossing the opposite way.
